---
title: Vegan Mushroom “MLT” Sandos with Roasted Potato Wedges & Mixed Green Salad
description: We’re giving this classic summery sandwich a vegan makeover. You’ll sizzle sliced mushrooms with savory-sweet paprika for extra-delicious flavor, and pile them onto toasted sourdough along with fresh tomato slices, mixed greens, and a swipe of tangy vegan mayo. Roasted potato wedges and a simple green salad round out this plant-based plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66b14d5f78d91450badf8142-5601a8a0.jpeg
